panels.name: Top NAS IP Addresses for Auth
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=<REPLACEME> (tacacs)
| parse "<*>*,* * Tacacs Logs * * * Common.Username=*,Common.Service=*,Common.Roles=*, [*],RADIUS.Auth-Source=*,RADIUS.Auth-Method=*,Common.System-Posture-Token=*,Common.Enforcement-Profiles=*, *,Common.Host-MAC-Address=*,Common.NAS-IP-Address=*,Common.Error-Code=*,Common.Request-Timestamp=*" as msg_id,throw1,throw2,internal_ip,msg_num,throw3,throw4,username,service,roles,status,auth_source,auth_method,sys_posture_token,enforcement_profiles,device_type,host_mac,nas_ip,error_code,request_timestamp
| fields - throw1, throw2, throw3, throw4 | count nas_ip | top 10 nas_ip by _count
